'''特什拜尼'''（{{Lang-hy|Կարմիր Բլուր}}）是古代[[烏拉爾圖|烏拉爾圖]]王國高加索省的首府，靠近[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]]首都[[葉里溫|葉里溫]]。特什拜尼曾經是一座城堡，整座城市面積{{convert|110|acre|km2}}<ref>Sir Banister Fletcher's a History of Architecture - Page 74 by Sir Banister Fletcher</ref>。特什拜尼位於海拔高度{{convert|901|m}}處<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://elevationmap.net/markvart-st-yerevan-armenia?latlngs=%2840.15318,44.451164999999946%29 |title=Teishebaini Elevation and Position |access-date=2015-12-17 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922200849/https://elevationmap.net/markvart-st-yerevan-armenia?latlngs=%2840.15318,44.451164999999946%29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
